    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predictions within acceptance thresholds across all primary QoIs. The relative hemolysis index at worst-case operating conditions (RH = 0.81) satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with margin. Uncertainty is discussed qualitatively in validation reports; while aleatory sources including inter-lot biological variability and specimen manufacturing scatter are acknowledged in narrative, the structured evidence package characterizes uncertainty quantification for the majority of validation results. The assessment team accepts the model as credible for the stated COU.",
